#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn3.2"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn3.2:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.2:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. Shackles "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn3.2:0.3"
msgid "2. Purisasutta "
msgstr "2. A Person "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.162, sc1
msgctxt "sn3.2:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.2:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho rājā pasenadi kosalo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho rājā pasenadi kosalo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then King Pasenadi of Kosala went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "sn3.2:1.3"
msgid "“kati nu kho, bhante, purisassa dhammā ajjhattaṃ uppajjamānā uppajjanti ahitāya dukkhāya aphāsuvihārāyā”ti? "
msgstr "“Sir, how many things arise inside a person for their harm, suffering, and discomfort?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn3.2:2.1"
msgid "“Tayo kho, mahārāja, purisassa dhammā ajjhattaṃ uppajjamānā uppajjanti ahitāya dukkhāya aphāsuvihārāya. "
msgstr "“Great king, three things arise inside a person for their harm, suffering, and discomfort. "

msgctxt "sn3.2:2.2"
msgid "Katame tayo? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "sn3.2:2.3"
msgid "Lobho kho, mahārāja, purisassa dhammo ajjhattaṃ uppajjamāno uppajjati ahitāya dukkhāya aphāsuvihārāya. "
msgstr "Greed, "

msgctxt "sn3.2:2.4"
msgid "Doso kho, mahārāja, purisassa dhammo ajjhattaṃ uppajjamāno uppajjati ahitāya dukkhāya aphāsuvihārāya. "
msgstr "hate, "

msgctxt "sn3.2:2.5"
msgid "Moho kho, mahārāja, purisassa dhammo ajjhattaṃ uppajjamāno uppajjati ahitāya dukkhāya aphāsuvihārāya. "
msgstr "and delusion. "

msgctxt "sn3.2:2.6"
msgid "Ime kho, mahārāja, tayo purisassa dhammā ajjhattaṃ uppajjamānā uppajjanti ahitāya dukkhāya aphāsuvihārāyā”ti. "
msgstr "These three things arise inside a person for their harm, suffering, and discomfort.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.2:2.7"
msgid "Idamavoca … pe … "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. … "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.163, sc3
msgctxt "sn3.2:3.1"
msgid "“Lobho doso ca moho ca, "
msgstr "“When greed, hate, and delusion, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.2:3.2"
msgid "purisaṃ pāpacetasaṃ; "
msgstr "have arisen inside oneself, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.2:3.3"
msgid "Hiṃsanti attasambhūtā, "
msgstr "they harm a person of wicked heart, "

# NOTE: See BB for readings.
#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: samphalan”ti → sapphalanti (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn3.2:3.4"
msgid "tacasāraṃva samphalan”ti. "
msgstr "as a reed is destroyed by its own fruit.”"

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
